The paper deals with the issue of bias in recommender systems, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper proposes a novel approach to address this issue by using pseudo labeling, which is a technique commonly used in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
